Cat
-Initiate to starting position on game start

-If Left mouse clicked, set orientation left and take ten steps forward
-If Right mouse clicked, set orientation right and take ten steps forward


Mouse
-Initiate to starting positions on game start
-Move 10 steps down on each tick
-When reach bottom of screen, reduce lives variable and reset position

-If event ballMoved Received, check for ballhit (ball position within cat position dimensions)
-If ballHit, increment Hit Count variable and reset mouse position

Ball
-When space clicked, set position x,y to equals cat position
-Move ten steps up with every tick
-Broadcast ball moved event with every tick
-Stop moving when reached top


Finished Project:
https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/245422629/
